attributes.title: Dissatisfied and disappointed
attributes.review: I was so excited to finally get this app so I could stay up to date on what is going on in the world around me. And honestly to look at more hot pictures of trump and his son. I was quickly disappointed as soon as I opened the app. first off, the app has a terrible layout and weird pop ups that ask for my kik username. it also took me more than an hour to even find one photo of Barron? Please have some decency to feed my addiction. I will never vote for trump again wholeheartedly because this app is so terrible and offensive.
